PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?dog ( ( YEAR( ?dod ) - YEAR( ?dob ) ) + ( MONTH( ?dod ) - MONTH( ?dob ) ) / 12 + ( DAY( ?dod ) - DAY( ?dob ) ) / 365.25 AS ?years ) WHERE {
  ?dog wdt:P31 wd:Q144 ; wdt:P569 ?dob ; wdt:P570 ?dod .
  FILTER ( ?dod > ?dob )
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?years )
OFFSET 1
LIMIT 1
